residents in beijing but many americans fled beijing when the army 
moved in and only about 200 people attended the bash compared with 
1500 last year 
eight chinese police with submachine guns took up posts outside 
the embassy but refused to say why they were there they may have 
hoped for an appearance by dissident fang lizhi and his wife who 
are wanted by police and have been hiding at the embassy 
