traditional clambake hickox saidwhat this does is allow them to 
do something that appears very complex in their own back yard 
while the food cooks the students sample clam chowder and crab 
cakes made earlier in the day less than an hour later bake master 
thad gruczka tests the cooking time by sticking a knife in the 
nearest potato 
if the potatoes are done the bake is done said gruczka 
chairman of the science department at south kingstown high school 
final exam the taste test 
when it comes to seafood there just isnt any better eating 
than a bake said fred creighton 19 
