a former exxon computer operator said he 
accidentally erased computer copies of thousands of documents on the 
alaskan oil spill according to the new york times 
an exxon spokesman confirmed the destruction but said company 
lawyers believe other copies exist either on paper or in other 
computer files the newspaper said in sunday editions 
