countrys biggest organizers of fireworks shows says intermediaries 
that handle his companys purchases abroad have advised grucci not 
to panic nonetheless the bellport nybased fireworks by grucci 
inc expects a slowdown in chinese production 
weve already placed our purchase orders to china now to try 
to beat the rush grucci said we usually dont make big orders 
until august or september to overseas 
firms like grucci that specialize in aerial displays dont rely 
on china as much as companies do that primarily provide fireworks 
for consumer use besides what it imports from china grucci 
supplements its own products with fireworks from numerous foreign 
sources including japan taiwan and other far eastern countries as 
well as ones in europe 
royce trout of atlas enterprises inc in fort worth texas a 
