<TEXT>
recent events show that in modern business 
unlike modern warfare defeated soldiers often rise to fight again 
another day 
indicted but undaunted junkbond king michael milken announced 
june 15 the day of his resignation from drexel burnham lambert 
inc that he was striking out on his own in a new firm 
