38180 while july silver settled at 5155 a troy ounce down from 
5338 
august crude oil rose to 2027 a barrel from 1971 a week 
earlier july heating oil fell to 4935 cents a gallon from 4949 
cents and unleaded gasoline for delivery in july settled at 5991 
cents a gallon down from 6292 cents 
